{"contents": ["<div class=\"content clear-block\">    \n    <p><strong><span class=\"blue-left-arrow\">Le 26/01, le service BatCub sera assur\u00e9 comme suit :<br></span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Parcours\u00a0<strong>Lormont Bas</strong> &gt;<strong>Les Hangars</strong> &gt;<strong>Quinconces</strong> assur\u00e9 toutes les<strong> 60 minutes </strong>de 07h \u00e0 19h.<span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet, 'Regular Sans', 'Liberation Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #3a403e;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 19.1875px;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;\"> <br><strong>De 9h00 \u00e0 10h00 : RAVITAILLEMENT et interruption du parcours</strong><br></span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>* Parcours\u00a0<strong>Stalingrad </strong>&gt;<strong>Quinconces</strong> assur\u00e9 toutes les\u00a0<strong>15 minutes</strong>\u00a0en heures de pointe (07h-09h, 12h-14h, 17h-19h) </li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li>* Parcours\u00a0<strong>Stalingrad </strong>&gt;<strong>Quinconces </strong>&gt;<strong>Les Hangars</strong> assur\u00e9 toutes les<strong>\u00a045 minutes</strong> en heures creuses (09h-12h et 14h-17h)<span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet, 'Regular Sans', 'Liberation Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #3a403e;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 19.1875px;\">\u00a0</span></span><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet, 'Regular Sans', 'Liberation Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #3a403e;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 19.1875px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Trebuchet, 'Regular Sans', 'Liberation Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #3a403e;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 19.1875px;\">\u00a0</span></span><br></strong></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>\u00a0*    Parcours assur\u00e9 par un bateau ne pouvant accueillir les usagers  en      fauteuils roulants, ni les v\u00e9los et \u00e9tant limit\u00e9 \u00e0 45 personnes.</em></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><br>Horaires donn\u00e9s \u00e0 titre indicatif :</span></p>\n<p>\u00a0</p>\n<p><img src=\"/sites/default/files/u48067/Liaison%201%20de%20%209h%20%C3%A0%2010h.JPG\" alt=\"Horaires BatCub\" title=\"Horaires BatCub\" width=\"535\" height=\"257\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><br></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"yellow-left-arrow\">Pour vous rendre de <strong>Lormont Bas aux Quinconces :<br></strong></span><br>Prendre la <strong>Lianes 7 </strong>\u00e0 l'arr\u00eat \"Lormont Bas\" (direction <em>Bordeaux Centre Commercial du Lac</em>) et descendre \u00e0 l'arr\u00eat \"Bassins  \u00e0 Flot\" puis correspondance avec le <strong>Tram B</strong> (direction <em>Pessac</em>/<em>France Alouette</em>) et  descendre \u00e0 l'arr\u00eat \"Cours du M\u00e9doc\" ou \"Quinconces\".</p>\n<p><em>Nous vous remercions de votre compr\u00e9hension.</em></p>\n          </div>"]}
